<div id="nodeDecoration"><h1 id="nodeTitle">4.4. Pérdidas Por Deterioro De Créditos Por Insolvencias (Art. 13 LIS)</h1></div>
<div class="iDevice_wrapper FreeTextIdevice" id="id15">
<div class="iDevice emphasis0">
<div id="ta15_85" class="block iDevice_content">
<div class="SCX265157610">
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCX265157610">
<p style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: 'Segoe UI',Tahoma,Verdana,'Sans-Serif'; background-color: transparent; color: windowtext; text-align: justify; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; text-indent: 14px; font-size: 6pt;" class="Paragraph SCX265157610"><span class="TextRun SCX265157610" style="color: #202020; background-color: #f4f4f4; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; line-height: 29px;" lang="ES-ES"><span style="background-color: inherit;" class="NormalTextRun SCX265157610">Serán deducibles las pérdidas por deterioro de las existencias y los créditos derivadas de las posibles </span></span><span class="TextRun Underlined SCX265157610" style="color: #2286c2; background-color: #f4f4f4; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; text-decoration: underline; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; line-height: 29px;" lang="ES-ES"><span style="background-color: inherit;" class="SpellingError SCX265157610">Insolvencias</span></span><span class="TextRun SCX265157610" style="color: #202020; background-color: #f4f4f4; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; line-height: 29px;" lang="ES-ES"><span style="background-color: inherit;" class="SpellingError SCX265157610">de</span></span><span class="TextRun SCX265157610" style="color: #202020; background-color: #f4f4f4; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; line-height: 29px;" lang="ES-ES"><span style="background-color: inherit;" class="NormalTextRun SCX265157610"> los deudores, cuando en el momento del devengo del Impuesto concurra alguna de las siguientes circunstancias:</span></span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 29px; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif;" class="EOP SCX265157610"> </span></p>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCX265157610">
<p style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: 'Segoe UI',Tahoma,Verdana,'Sans-Serif'; background-color: transparent; color: windowtext; text-align: justify; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; text-indent: 14px; font-size: 6pt;" class="Paragraph SCX265157610"></p>
<img src="https://word-edit.officeapps.live.com/we/ResReader.ashx?v=00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000014&amp;n=E2o378.img&amp;rndm=44995abf-c4cf-42b8-b2b1-4c1c58c8e5f6&amp;WOPIsrc=https%3A%2F%2Fwopi%2Dtest%2Edropbox%2Ecom%2Fwopi%2Ffiles%2FjEkD7fE%5F8fAAAAAAAAAA3g&amp;access_token=NTE4NTY3OGEtNWQxNC00ZTVhLWExZTQtMzEzZGVkZjhlMjFm&amp;access_token_ttl=1464941540453&amp;usid=2d63077c-d8da-45f8-bca6-f57db9d0e233&amp;build=16.0.6927.2251&amp;waccluster=NL1" style="width: auto; height: auto;" alt="Impuesto sobre Sociedades" class="WACImage SCX265157610" /><span class="TextRun EmptyTextRun SCX265157610" style="color: #000000; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; line-height: 29px;" lang="ES-ES"></span><span style="font-size: 11pt; line-height: 29px; font-family: Arial,sans-serif;" class="EOP SCX265157610"> </span></div>
<ul class="BulletListStyle1 SCX265157610">
<li style="margin-left: 48px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal;" class="OutlineElement Ltr SCX265157610">
<p style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: 'Segoe UI',Tahoma,Verdana,'Sans-Serif'; background-color: transparent; color: windowtext; text-align: justify; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; text-indent: 0px; font-size: 6pt;" class="Paragraph SCX265157610"><span class="TextRun SCX265157610" style="color: #202020; background-color: #f4f4f4; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; line-height: 29px;" lang="ES-ES"><span style="background-color: inherit;" class="NormalTextRun SCX265157610">Que haya transcurrido el plazo de 6 meses desde el vencimiento de la obligación.</span></span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 29px; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif;" class="EOP SCX265157610"> </span></p>
</li>
<li style="margin-left: 48px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal;" class="OutlineElement Ltr SCX265157610">
<p style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: 'Segoe UI',Tahoma,Verdana,'Sans-Serif'; background-color: transparent; color: windowtext; text-align: justify; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; text-indent: 0px; font-size: 6pt;" class="Paragraph SCX265157610"><span class="TextRun SCX265157610" style="color: #202020; background-color: #f4f4f4; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; line-height: 29px;" lang="ES-ES"><span style="background-color: inherit;" class="NormalTextRun SCX265157610">Que el deudor esté declarado en situación de concurso.</span></span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 29px; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif;" class="EOP SCX265157610"> </span></p>
</li>
<li style="margin-left: 48px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal;" class="OutlineElement Ltr SCX265157610">
<p style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: 'Segoe UI',Tahoma,Verdana,'Sans-Serif'; background-color: transparent; color: windowtext; text-align: justify; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; text-indent: 0px; font-size: 6pt;" class="Paragraph SCX265157610"><span class="TextRun SCX265157610" style="color: #202020; background-color: #f4f4f4; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; line-height: 29px;" lang="ES-ES"><span style="background-color: inherit;" class="NormalTextRun SCX265157610">Que el deudor esté procesado por el delito de alzamiento de bienes.</span></span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 29px; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif;" class="EOP SCX265157610"> </span></p>
</li>
<li style="margin-left: 48px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal;" class="OutlineElement Ltr SCX265157610">
<p style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: 'Segoe UI',Tahoma,Verdana,'Sans-Serif'; background-color: transparent; color: windowtext; text-align: justify; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; text-indent: 0px; font-size: 6pt;" class="Paragraph SCX265157610"><span class="TextRun SCX265157610" style="color: #202020; background-color: #f4f4f4; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; line-height: 29px;" lang="ES-ES"><span style="background-color: inherit;" class="NormalTextRun SCX265157610">Que las obligaciones hayan sido reclamadas judicialmente o sean objeto de un litigio judicial o procedimiento arbitral de cuya solución dependa su cobro.</span></span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 29px; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif;" class="EOP SCX265157610"> </span></p>
</li>
</ul>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCX265157610">
<p style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: 'Segoe UI',Tahoma,Verdana,'Sans-Serif'; background-color: transparent; color: windowtext; text-align: justify; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; text-indent: 14px; font-size: 6pt;" class="Paragraph SCX265157610"><span class="TextRun SCX265157610" style="color: #202020; background-color: #f4f4f4; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; line-height: 29px;" lang="ES-ES"><span style="background-color: inherit;" class="NormalTextRun SCX265157610">No serán deducibles las pérdidas por deterioro de créditos:</span></span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 29px; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif;" class="EOP SCX265157610"> </span></p>
</div>
<ul class="BulletListStyle1 SCX265157610">
<li style="margin-left: 48px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal;" class="OutlineElement Ltr SCX265157610">
<p style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: 'Segoe UI',Tahoma,Verdana,'Sans-Serif'; background-color: transparent; color: windowtext; text-align: justify; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; text-indent: 0px; font-size: 6pt;" class="Paragraph SCX265157610"><span class="TextRun SCX265157610" style="color: #202020; background-color: #f4f4f4; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; line-height: 29px;" lang="ES-ES"><span style="background-color: inherit;" class="NormalTextRun SCX265157610">Los adeudados por entidades de derecho público.</span></span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 29px; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif;" class="EOP SCX265157610"> </span></p>
</li>
<li style="margin-left: 48px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal;" class="OutlineElement Ltr SCX265157610">
<p style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: 'Segoe UI',Tahoma,Verdana,'Sans-Serif'; background-color: transparent; color: windowtext; text-align: justify; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; text-indent: 0px; font-size: 6pt;" class="Paragraph SCX265157610"><span class="TextRun SCX265157610" style="color: #202020; background-color: #f4f4f4; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; line-height: 29px;" lang="ES-ES"><span style="background-color: inherit;" class="NormalTextRun SCX265157610">Las correspondientes a créditos adeudados por personas o entidades vincula­das, salvo que estén en situación de concurso y se haya producido la apertura de la fase de liquidación por el juez, en los términos establecidos en la Ley 22/2003, de 9 de julio, Concursal.</span></span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 29px; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif;" class="EOP SCX265157610"> </span></p>
</li>
<li style="margin-left: 48px; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal;" class="OutlineElement Ltr SCX265157610">
<p style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: 'Segoe UI',Tahoma,Verdana,'Sans-Serif'; background-color: transparent; color: windowtext; text-align: justify; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; text-indent: 0px; font-size: 6pt;" class="Paragraph SCX265157610"><span class="TextRun SCX265157610" style="color: #202020; background-color: #f4f4f4; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; line-height: 29px;" lang="ES-ES"><span style="background-color: inherit;" class="NormalTextRun SCX265157610">Las correspondientes a estimaciones globales del riesgo de insolvencias de clientes y deudores.</span></span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 29px; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif;" class="EOP SCX265157610"> </span></p>
</li>
</ul>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCX265157610">
<p style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: 'Segoe UI',Tahoma,Verdana,'Sans-Serif'; background-color: transparent; color: #666666; text-align: justify; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; text-indent: 14px; font-size: 6pt;" role="heading" class="Paragraph SCX265157610"><span class="TextRun SCX265157610" style="color: #202020; background-color: #f4f4f4; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none; font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; line-height: 28px;" lang="ES-ES"><span style="background-color: inherit;" class="NormalTextRun SCX265157610">Ejemplo:</span></span><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; line-height: 28px; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif;" class="EOP SCX265157610"> </span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="SCX265157610">
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCX265157610">
<p style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: 'Segoe UI',Tahoma,Verdana,'Sans-Serif'; background-color: transparent; color: windowtext; text-align: justify; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; text-indent: 14px; font-size: 6pt;" class="Paragraph SCX265157610"><span class="TextRun SCX265157610" style="color: #202020; background-color: #f4f4f4; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; line-height: 29px;" lang="ES-ES"><span style="background-color: inherit;" class="NormalTextRun SCX265157610">Una sociedad presenta esta información en relación a la dotación a la pérdida por deterioro por insolvencias.</span></span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 29px; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif;" class="EOP SCX265157610"> </span></p>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCX265157610">
<p style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: 'Segoe UI',Tahoma,Verdana,'Sans-Serif'; background-color: transparent; color: windowtext; text-align: justify; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; text-indent: 0px; font-size: 6pt;" class="Paragraph SCX265157610"><span class="TextRun SCX265157610" style="color: #000000; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; line-height: 29px;" lang="ES-ES"><span style="background-color: inherit;" class="NormalTextRun SCX265157610"></span></span><span style="font-size: 11pt; line-height: 29px; font-family: Arial,sans-serif;" class="EOP SCX265157610"> </span></p>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCX265157610">
<p style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: 'Segoe UI',Tahoma,Verdana,'Sans-Serif'; background-color: transparent; color: windowtext; text-align: justify; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; text-indent: 14px; font-size: 6pt;" class="Paragraph SCX265157610"></p>
